query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.role, p.equityPercentage, p.revenueSharePercentage, p.lifetimeAccess, p.grantedAt, t.transactionId, t.timestamp 
FROM partners p 
LEFT JOIN transactions t ON t.partnerId = p.id 
ORDER BY p.id;
